  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of Fractional Flow Reserve versus instant Wave-Free Ratio for assessment of
      coronary artery stenosis severity in routine practice

        -  To compare FFR to iFR in arbitrary consecutive patients referred for percutaneous
           coronary intervention (PCI).

        -  To investigate the influence of hyperemia on iFR.

        -  To test reproducibility of iFR and FFR.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
